# Feature 0055: keep recorder snapshot shell libs (not a Python build dir).
# Whitelist the dir, re-ignore everything inside, then whitelist only *.sh.
# Any non-shell artifact dropped here (logs, tmp files) stays ignored.
!scripts/phase4/lib/
scripts/phase4/lib/*
!scripts/phase4/lib/*.sh
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

